   "Software" means the NetWatch source code, binaries, documentation,
   and all associated files in this repository.

   "Individual Use" means use by a single natural person on their own
   personal device(s) for personal, educational, or non-commercial
   security monitoring purposes.

   "Commercial Use" means any use of the Software by or on behalf of a
   company, organisation, institution, or other legal entity, including
   but not limited to: deployment on company-owned or company-managed
   devices, use as part of a managed service, integration into a
   commercial product, or use by contractors or employees as part of
   their work responsibilities.

   "Seat" means one installation of the Software on one device or
   for one user within a Commercial Use context.


